\pard\plain \tx360\tx720\tx1080\tx1440\tx1800\tx2160\tx2880\tx3600\tx4320\fi360\sl264\slmult1\ltrch\loch {\f0\fs26\b0\i0\ul\ulc0\cf1 KEY THEMATIC CONCEPTS for a modern story or game}
\par\plain \f0\fs26\b0\i0\cf1
\par\plain {\f0\fs26\b0\i0\cf1 There are some key concepts that anyone living in the real world in modern times is concerned with.  Finding ways to explore these themes in the story, in a meaningful way that leaves room for multiple interpretations and movements, would be a big win. }
\par\plain \f0\fs26\b0\i0\cf1
\par\plain {\f0\fs26\b0\i0\cf1 These include:}
\par\plain \f0\fs26\b0\i0\cf1
\par\plain {\f0\fs26\b0\i0\cf1 * Love}
\par\plain {\f0\fs26\b0\i0\cf1 * Ethics}
\par\plain {\f0\fs26\b0\i0\cf1 * Self-sacrifice}
\par\plain {\f0\fs26\b0\i0\cf1 * Duty}
\par\plain {\f0\fs26\b0\i0\cf1 * Healing}
\par\plain \f0\fs26\b0\i0\cf1
\par\plain {\f0\fs26\b0\i0\cf1 "Do humans deserve to live on this planet that they have done so much to ruin?" -- pretty much the overarching philosophical theme of the epic.  What is this character doing (or not) to reverse the ecocide?}
\par\plain \f0\fs26\b0\i0\cf1
\par\plain {\f0\fs26\b0\i0\cf1 When working through characters, episodes and story arcs, but especially characters and episodes, include notes on these items. They have been added to the Character template. }
